title: of the Act of 1992 shall come into operation for the District Court sitting in
heading: 1. (1) This Order may be cited as the Criminal Evidence Act 1992
text_raw:
1. (1) This Order may be cited as the Criminal Evidence Act 1992 

(Sections 13 and 16) (Commencement) Order 2023. 

(2) In this Order, “Act of 1992” means the Criminal Evidence Act 1992 

(No. 12 of 1992).
